n products and producers, aligning with the Department\\u2019s mission, and ensure the sustainability of our marketing efforts without compromising our already stretched budget. By enhancing our ability to promote local agriculture, this support is crucial for the continued success of our initiatives benefiting New Mexican farmers and producers.\",\"expected_reach\":\"Print Distribution: 18,000 copies per issue | 63,000 estimated readers per issue | 120+ locations across NM, including 90 with branded racks | True 99% pickup rate\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2025-06-04 23:15:20','2025-04-22 21:04:59','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(21,214,179,'advertising','approved','2025',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"77d7bf90-f815-4d85-b77e-9bad116f4b5c\",\"company_name\":\"County Line Feed & Supply\",\"admin_initials\":\"SP\",\"date_submitted\":\"2025-01-10 21:24:34\",\"date_approved\":\"2025-01-13 17:59:48\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Radio\",\"media_type_other\":\"\",\"funding_explanation\":\"New radio add, investing more to reach new potential customers, also addvertising being a member with the NMDA New Mexico Grown with Tradition and Taste the Tradtion. \",\"expected_reach\":\"Albuquerque Metro Area\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2025-01-13 17:59:48','2025-01-10 21:24:34','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(22,281,289,'advertising','approved','2024',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"819a299b-e832-4e67-9c04-48abb0572d1f\",\"company_name\":\"Full Circle Mushrooms\",\"admin_initials\":\"DS\",\"date_submitted\":\"2024-06-10 18:20:46\",\"date_approved\":\"2024-06-14 16:44:12\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Other\",\"media_type_other\":\"Printed Magazine\",\"funding_explanation\":\"Full Circle Mushrooms is the only source of funding for this advertisement and we currently don\'t have enough money to cover it in full.\\\\nWe see this magazine as a great opportunity to reach new targeted costumers and build a strong brand and awareness about mushrooms being grown in New Mexico.\",\"expected_reach\":\"18K magazines printed 6 times a year reach 63K* readers per issue and 378K annually.\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2024-06-14 16:44:12','2024-06-10 18:20:46','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(23,231,132,'advertising','rejected','2024',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"95aee478-5521-48d2-82d1-a6fe155032c5\",\"company_name\":\"Cibolo Junction Food & Spice Co. \",\"admin_initials\":\"\",\"date_submitted\":\"2024-06-06 22:20:10\",\"date_approved\":\"\",\"date_rejected\":\"2024-06-10 20:31:08\",\"media_type\":\"Other\",\"media_type_other\":\"\'Tote\' Bags as give-away promo materials to grocery store buyers\",\"funding_explanation\":\"Funding for the Cibolo Junction tote bags would not substitute private funds because it would cover additional costs beyond our current budget, allowing us to produce and distribute more bags to promote local agriculture and sustainability. This funding would supplement our efforts, enabling a broader reach and greater impact without replacing the private funds already allocated.\",\"expected_reach\":\"100 - 1000 (depending how much the tote bag is used around town per recipient)\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2024-06-10 20:31:08','2024-06-06 22:20:10','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(24,313,92,'advertising','submitted','2025',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"a3ff82f9-e40d-4cca-a9f9-249da02ff7dc\",\"company_name\":\"A & M MEAT PROCESSING\",\"admin_initials\":\"\",\"date_submitted\":\"2025-08-21 15:48:46\",\"date_approved\":\"\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Radio\",\"media_type_other\":\"\",\"funding_explanation\":\"Any funding we receive for radio advertising would not be a substitution for private funds. Our business advertising budget is limited and already allocated to essential, routine marketing efforts such as social media promotion and in-store outreach. Radio advertising is an expanded effort designed to reach a broader audience, strengthen community awareness, and increase consumer access to locally processed meats. Without outside support, this type of outreach would not be financially feasible at the scale needed. Grant funds would therefore supplement\\u2014not replace\\u2014our existing resources and allow us to expand visibility in a way that private funds alone could not cover.\",\"expected_reach\":\"17000 a day\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,NULL,'2025-08-21 15:48:46','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(25,276,128,'advertising','approved','2025',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"a42fa0f2-846f-4029-90e4-d47338b8d385\",\"company_name\":\"Gilly Loco \",\"admin_initials\":\"SP\",\"date_submitted\":\"2025-05-15 21:25:10\",\"date_approved\":\"2025-06-04 23:34:05\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Non-Organic Social Media Posts\\/Campaign\",\"media_type_other\":\"\",\"funding_explanation\":\"This funding will allow us to scale efforts that wouldn\\u2019t be possible without it! \",\"expected_reach\":\"200,000\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2025-06-04 23:34:05','2025-05-15 21:25:10','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(26,296,121,'advertising','rejected','2024',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"ac402ef4-0113-4d21-a01e-341e7658e47a\",\"company_name\":\"AlbuKirky Seasonings LLC\",\"admin_initials\":\"\",\"date_submitted\":\"2024-06-09 16:35:11\",\"date_approved\":\"\",\"date_rejected\":\"2024-06-10 20:28:57\",\"media_type\":\"Non-Organic Social Media Posts\\/Campaign\",\"media_type_other\":\"\",\"funding_explanation\":\"I have already paid for the production of the ads. Any funds received will be used to offset that cost and fund the next round of ad production.\",\"expected_reach\":\"100K-150K Impressions per month\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2024-06-10 20:28:57','2024-06-09 16:35:11','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(27,398,26,'advertising','approved','2025',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"b76ea3a4-c7bb-447a-b2f4-4d5011f08f05\",\"company_name\":\"Big Jim Farms\",\"admin_initials\":\"SP\",\"date_submitted\":\"2025-05-14 23:04:17\",\"date_approved\":\"2025-08-04 21:05:27\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Other\",\"media_type_other\":\"Farmers Market Tent w\\/ Logos\",\"funding_explanation\":\"Any funding received would not be substituting private funds because the scale and visibility of this project go beyond what our current resources can support. We do not have private funds allocated for this type of infrastructure, and the grant would enable us to invest in a high-quality, durable setup that enhances our presence at public events and on our farm.\\\\n\\\\nThe project involves the purchase of customizable pop-up tents that will feature our custom logo and branding. These tents will be used at all our events to create a professional and cohesive appearance, improve functionality, and strengthen brand recognition in the community.\\\\n\\\\nWe will use the tents to prominently display our \\u201cTaste the Tradition\\u201d and \\u201cGrown with Tradition\\u201d logos at a wide range of events. We currently attend three large farmers markets weekly\\u2014Downtown Growers\\u2019 Market, Uptown Winrock Market, and the Railyards Market\\u2014as well as other major community events, including Earth Day Festival, Lavender Festival, Balloon Fiesta, ristra demonstrations at the Albuquerque Tramway during Balloon Fiesta, Summer Fest, Spring Festival at the Rio Grande Nature Center, and many more.\\\\n\\\\nIn addition, the tents will be used at our farm, which is open six months out of the year and draws thousands of visitors each season. We host large events during the fall and holiday seasons, and the tents will be used consistently throughout our open season for workshops, classes, field trips, and much more. The tents will also serve as the backdrop for live musicians who perform at our events, creating a lively atmosphere and offering photo opportunities that are shared widely on social media. They will also be used weekly by our chef for food preparation during our farm-to-table dinners. The tents will serve as both a functional asset and a powerful promotional tool across all our public engagements.\",\"expected_reach\":\"The expected reach and impressions of this advertising effort are substantial, as the tents will be used consistently at high-traffic events such as three weekly farmers markets, major festivals like the Balloon Fiesta, and seasonal activities at our farm, which draws thousands of visitors annually. Each event attracts hundreds to thousands of attendees, including both local residents and out-of-town visitors. With the tents prominently displaying our branding, we anticipate reaching thousands of individuals each season, with additional exposure through social media as attendees share photos featuring the tents. Over the 3 to 5-year lifespan of the tents, the total reach will extend well into the hundreds of thousands, both through direct interaction at events and through online impressions.\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2025-08-04 21:05:27','2025-05-14 23:04:17','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(28,221,164,'advertising','approved','2024',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"b79a1a24-9371-4bce-8843-298aa4a15e36\",\"company_name\":\"Snugglecubs Cookies\",\"admin_initials\":\"DS\",\"date_submitted\":\"2024-06-09 21:08:10\",\"date_approved\":\"2024-06-17 19:07:46\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Other\",\"media_type_other\":\"Banner\",\"funding_explanation\":\"New banner highlights Taste the Tradition logo on our new 4x10\' banner that we use for events.\",\"expected_reach\":\"3-10k per event\",\"advertising_costs\":\"\"}','[]','',NULL,'2024-06-17 19:07:46','2024-06-09 21:08:10','2025-11-21 18:29:27'),(29,231,132,'advertising','approved','2024',NULL,NULL,'{\"legacy_id\":\"baf3fcfc-9e23-4366-99d3-e6af95b7cd51\",\"company_name\":\"Cibolo Junction Food & Spice Co. \",\"admin_initials\":\"DS\",\"date_submitted\":\"2024-06-06 22:15:08\",\"date_approved\":\"2024-06-17 16:24:43\",\"date_rejected\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"Other\",\"media_type_other\