0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>new feature: import previews</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: restore gallery migration support</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: preserve legitimate double quotes from Excel files</li>\r\n<li>maintenance: update PhpSpreadsheet and phpseclib</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.7</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>improvement: upgrade svg-sanitize library</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.6</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>security improvement: fixes CVE-2025-10001</li>\r\n<li>improvement: upgrade PhpSpreadsheet version</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.5</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: import settings file upload doesn\'t work</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.4</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>improvement: streamlined new/existing items UI</li>\r\n<li>improvement: add alternative Excel processing for files that fail with PhpSpreadsheet</li>\r\n<li>improvement: add drag and drop file uploads to step 1 of a new import</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.3</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>improvement: add partner discounts</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: resolve textdomain notices</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.2</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>improvement: streamlined \'new import\' flow to make filter configuration step optional</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: taxonomy \'only add new\' option only works with 1 record per iteration</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.1</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: don\'t set defaults for TEXT db fields</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.11.0</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>security improvement: migrate from PHPExcel to PhpSpreadsheet</li>\r\n<li>API: add \'pmxi_accept_header\' filter</li>\r\n<li>improvement: UI updates</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.10.1</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>integration: support sending Function Editor code to WPCodeBox</li>\r\n<li>API: add \'pmxi_mimic_browser_user_agent\' filter</li>\r\n<li>API: add \'pmxi_user_agent\' filter</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: \'current_xml_node\' value is missing for image filters in some cases</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: type error in rare cases when uploading Excel file</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.10.0</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>API: add pmxi_content_image action</li>\r\n<li>improvement: UI updates</li>\r\n<li>improvement: prioritize XML in the Accept list when downloading files</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: non-SVG images are passed to SVG sanitizer in some cases</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.9.11</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: terms without parent aren\'t matched correctly</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.9.10</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: updater class isn\'t called when updating plugins via WP-CLI</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: fatal error when deleting missing records</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.9.9</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: taxonomy terms are sometimes not found by slug</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: SQL query failure due to query length in rare cases when using \'change missing\' option</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: add-ons cannot set featured image/thumbnail in some cases</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.9.8</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>security improvement, fixes: CVE-2024-8722, CVE-2024-9664, CVE-2024-9661</li>\r\n</ul><h4>4.9.7</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP versio