:\"last_updated\";s:19:\"2025-10-29 01:21:15\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:56:\"https://www.wpallimport.com/downloads/wp-all-export-pro/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:2:{s:11:\"description\";s:164:\"<p>Learn more about WP All Export at <a href=\"http://www.wpallimport.com/export\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.wpallimport.com/export</a></p>\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:43361:\"<h4>1.9.13</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: scheduling modal shows wrong license status</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: restore missing ACF field sanitize method</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.12</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>fix: add missing placeholder for Latvian translation</li>\r\n<li>improvement: better handling of corrupt/unexpected data when exporting</li>\r\n<li>improvement: update PhpSpreadsheet</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.11</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>improvement: add support for exporting WooCommerce Guest Customers when using the User Export Add-On</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.10</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>improvement: add partner discounts</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: resolve textdomain notices</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.8</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>security improvement: migrate from PHPExcel to PhpSpreadsheet</li>\r\n<li>improvement: UI updates</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.7</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>integration: support sending Function Editor code to WPCodeBox</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.6</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\r\n<li>bug fix: failed opening required file</li>\r\n</ul><h4>1.9.5</h4><ul>\r\n<li>minimum WordPress version: 5.0</li>\r\n<li>minimum PHP version: 7.4</li>\